Welcome to the Christmas Eve Party in the Nutcracker! I really hope you enjoy walking through this room as much as I enjoyed decorating it!
.

ALSO! There is a Grinch crashing the party! Can you find him? 😉

node.text:
See if you can count the correct number of nutcrackers in this room (entryway and staircase) to be entered for a chance to win 1 of 30 Starbucks gift cards we’re giving out tomorrow! Also, if you’d prefer an Amazon gift card, that can be arranged 😉

Steven, Kimmy, McKenna Kate and I had so much fun dreaming this up and building it together! We are definitely not pro’s when it comes to carpentry (or really any type of building😂), but the journey was a total blast!

Hope you enjoy watching this even half as much as we enjoyed creating it!!!😍

node.title: Welcome to Opening Night of The Nutcracker Ballet....aka the Entry Way!

node.text:
Through out this next week, I’ll be sharing the Christmas Decor through out the various rooms in our home!
.
As you know, our decor this year is inspired by the Nutcracker Ballet!!
.
Each room depicts a different scene from the Nutcracker, and just to make things even more fun, most of the rooms have a hidden item or two!
😉
.
I really hope you enjoy seeing the home as much as I enjoyed decorating it
😍
.
In the comments below, let me know which room you are most excited to see!!

node.title: Welcome to Day 1 of the Turtle Creek Lane 2020 Holiday Home Tour!!
